<subSubSection pageId="35" pageNumber="36" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,419,332,358]" box="[151,419,332,358]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,419,332,358]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,419,332,358]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<taxonomicName box="[151,242,332,358]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Agrotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="robusta">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,242,332,358]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">robusta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
-species group
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,1436,402,607]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
This species group is characterized by: in male genitalia tegumen with “shoulders” strongly marked; valve subrectangular, basal half narrow, then widened; cucullus apex strongly projected anterodorsally; sacculus 
<number box="[1347,1360,438,463]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" value="3.0">3</number>
/ 
<number box="[1369,1382,438,463]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" value="5.0">5</number>
× as wide as valve; saccus hemispherical, notched dorsally and ventrally projected as a spine. Aedeagus fully sclerotized; vesica long, 
<number box="[441,497,511,535]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" value="9.0" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="8.0">8–10</number>
× as long as aedeagus, excepting 
<taxonomicName box="[907,1019,510,535]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Agrotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ipsilon">
<emphasis box="[907,1019,510,535]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">A. ipsilon</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<number box="[1039,1054,510,535]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" value="6.0">6</number>
× as long as aedeagus). Female genitalia with appendix bursae long, 
<number box="[562,604,546,571]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" value="5.0" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="4.0">4–6</number>
× as long as corpus bursae, excepting 
<taxonomicName box="[1031,1138,546,571]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Agrotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ipsilon">
<emphasis box="[1031,1138,546,571]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">A. ipsilon</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(1.5– 
<number box="[1203,1217,546,571]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" value="2.0">2</number>
× as long as corpus bursae).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
